import logo from './logo.svg';
import './App.css';
import Home from '../../../UofA-VIRT-FSF-FT-05-2022-U-LOLC/22-State/01-Activities/18-Stu_JWT-Review/Solved/client/src/pages/Home';

function App() {
  return (
    <Router>
      <Header />
        <Routes>
          <Route
            path = '/'
            exact
            element ={<Home />}/>
          <Route
            path = '/20-REACTPortfolio'
            exact
            element ={<Game />}/>
          <Route
            path = "/AboutMe"
            element ={<AboutMe />}/>
            <Route
            path="/Portfolio"
            element={<Portfolio />}/>
            <Route
            path="/Resume"
            element={<Resume />}/>
            <Route
            path="/Contact"
            element={<Contact />}/>
        </Routes>
      <Footer />
    </Router>
  );
}

export default App;
